text: Inge Lindqvist (born 13 March 1935) is a Swedish ski jumper. He competed in the individual event at the 1960 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1935 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Sweden Category:Ski jumpers at the 1960 Winter Olympics Category:People from Eda Municipality
